item.title: CVE-2022-3335|2024-08-03T01:07:06.557Z -- unknown -- kadence%20woocommerce%20email%20designer
item.description: The Kadence WooCommerce Email Designer WordPress plugin before 1.5.7 unserialises the content of an imported file, which could lead to PHP object injections issues when an admin import (intentionally or not) a malicious file and a suitable gadget chain is present on the blog.
